data.description: If you're looking for a move-in ready Ranch, easy to maintain, no stairs, no basement, look no further! This home has 3 bedrooms, 1 large bathroom with double sinks, a den with a wood burning fireplace, eat in kitchen space, front living room, 1st floor laundry and a spacious fully fenced in back yard. Front deck newly installed as well as other updates. Ask about the $15,000 grant program!
